        <div class="col-lg-6">

            <h1 class="display-1 fw-bold text-uppercase">
                ENDLESS CUSTOMIZE
            </h1>

            <p class="lead mt-4">
                Create a controller that matches your style.<br>
                Pick from bold colors, unique designs, and more.
            </p>

            <a href="#" class="btn btn-light fw-bold px-4 py-3 mt-4">
